          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your<strong> lime[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Peel and roughly chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped shallot </strong>and<strong> chopped pepper</strong> to the dish</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1707995281114-x200.jpg",
