          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> tomato paste</strong>,<strong> </strong>your<strong> roasted garlic paste </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>smoky stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1707995288768-x200.jpg",
