            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to the dish with your<strong> basmati rice</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> smoky stock </strong>with your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>,<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, top with your <strong>hake fillet[s] </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1707995298172-x200.jpg",
