            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the rice is cooked and the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>one-pot hake & Mexican-style rice</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime quarters </strong>with a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> lime mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
