      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot hake & Mexican-style rice </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> lime mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions </strong>and a <strong>remaining lime quarter</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
